1. the index.tt template (and page) needs categories like:
	-> local articles
	-> external resources
	-> media 


The categories.tt file to be referenced in index.tt and the content files to be referenced in the categories:

index page 		< index.tt
	category1 		< category.tt
		- content1i		< content.tt 
		- content2
	category2  		< category.tt
		- content1		< content.tt
		- content2
